Class Beacon

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.estimote.coresdk.recognition.packets.Packet
      • com.estimote.coresdk.recognition.packets.Beacon
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable

    public class Beacon
extends Packet
    Immutable representations of single beacon.

    Two beacons are considered equal if their location UUID, major and minor are equal.

    Author:
    Wiktor Gworek (wiktor@estimote.com)
